Vital Point to Capture?(12)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par There is one eye in the corner.
\par So White only has to destroy the eye on the left.
\par One move decides this life and death problem.
\par
\par
\par }
