Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White can destroy the eye with 1.
\par It is an attack which \cf1\b aims\cf0\b0  at Black's \cf1\b shortage of liberties\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par After Black 2, White connects with 3 and Black is captured.
\par If White plays at A instead of 3, Black is still captured.
\par
\par }
