Dia. 02 Big Illusion
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White might think that playing at 1 is good too. After Black connects at 2, White attaches at 3 and it becomes the same with the correct answer in \b Dia. 01\b0 .
\par
\par However this is a \cf1\b big illusion\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Black can play at 3 instead of 2, then he \cf2\b lives\cf0\b0 .
\par }
