Dia. 04 Confused?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par People who thought about White 1 are probably \cf1\b confused\cf0\b0  with another situation.
\par
\par Black lives easily with many points up to 4.
\par
\par If there is a White stone at A, White 1 would be a great way to attack.
\par
\par }
